description:
Rachel is late again, coming home from work, dinner isn’t going to cook itself, & the house certainly doesn’t get cleaned up by itself either! Rachel’s job is getting in the way, this is not cutting it.
Oh here she is, finally! Oh poor Rachel Nova she feels like she is failing at her job, well guess what you’re failing at home too! Well I just reminded her, she has a job here too, to take care of me!
Now she is complaining about her boss, that he is a asshole, you know what I think, her boss
wants to fuck her, anytime a man bitches it means they want to fuck you. I mean, look at the fantastic shoes & sexy dress Rachel has on, for work! You know what, it’s time to say fuck you to the Boss & the Job & start taking care of me! Before all this going to work idea, you used to wear this chocker, well it’s time to put it back on, and start serving me! Oh & at the end our little session, I will actually serve you dinner!
title: Alura Jenson in Serve Me Rachel!
